snippet.textDisplay:
Fellow Smash players please listen carefuly to my wording. I understand why you are upset, but this was to be expected. FE is at its greatest right now. Three Houses was rated the second best game by both critics and players of 2019, it was also voted as a game that should have been at least mentioned as a possibility for best game of the year awards by the players. Byleth was a character who was a major role in a series unlike characters like Waluigi (who think is a awesome character), was made by people willing to let their character be in smash unlike the Cloud from Square Enix who was barely added, and was a character everyone would know. Just give Sakurai a break and stop yelling bloody murder! Many characters can be chosen but only few are a fit.
(Hollow Knight I hope will get a spot.)
